Homepage: https://github.com/Baraka-Malila/asusctl-ubuntu

Package: asus-suite
Architecture: all
Depends: asusctl (>= 6.3.8-1~noble1),
         supergfxctl (>= 5.2.7-1~noble1),
         utu,
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: asus-backlight-fix
Description: Full ASUS Linux control stack for Ubuntu 24.04 (meta-package)
 Installs asusd (system daemon), asusctl (CLI), supergfxd (GPU mode
 daemon), supergfxctl (GPU mode CLI), and the utu GTK4/libadwaita
 control centre. Single entry point for ASUS laptop users on Noble:
 .
   sudo apt install asus-suite
